This paper is about monitoring and analyzing data centers, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The paper also discusses the use of performance counters and power consumption as key metrics, which suggests a focus on Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) and Systems and Control (cs.SY). The paper also mentions the use of custom solutions for power consumption analysis, which could indicate a focus on Software Engineering (cs.SE) and Programming Languages (cs.PL) for developing these solutions.
